                INSERT INTO project (project_id, project_name)
                VALUES
                (
                    $1,
                    'My Project'
                )
            ),
            insert_warehouse AS (
                INSERT INTO warehouse (warehouse_id, warehouse_name, project_id, status, "tabular_delete_mode")
                VALUES
                (
                    $2,
                    'My Warehouse',
                    $1,
                    'active',
                    'hard'
                )
            )

                attempt,
                warehouse_id,
                queue_name,
                task_data,
                status,
                entity_id,
                entity_name,
                entity_type,
                project_id,
                attempt_scheduled_for,
                task_created_at,
                created_at
            )
            VALUES

                NULL,
                'clean_tasks',
                '{}'::jsonb,
                'success'::task_final_status,
                NULL,
                NULL,
                'project'::entity_type,

                now() - make_interval(days => ($6 + 5)::int),
                now() - make_interval(days => ($6 + 5)::int),
